    <item>
      <title>Who completes the program and why?</title>
      <link>/year1/making-it1/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Aug 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/year1/making-it1/</guid>
      <description>


&lt;p&gt;While there are many, many reasons that someone may not finish a PhD program, I think most of them can fit into one of three general areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style=&#34;list-style-type: decimal&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Match with “PhD life”&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Match with program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Allocation of effort&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In these slides, we’ll talk a bit more about these areas and what I think they mean.&lt;/p&gt;
